{"tid":434824,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2017-18 LIHKG香港女神總會盃第一圈投選專區(171014)","createTime":"2017-10-13T15:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T14:15:21.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"adc252924a15e14a323e6e0c1ff9c7a4e9463345","tid":434824,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T15:59:27.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:10am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n(甲)張沛樂v鄧洢玲(非)<br />\n(冠)黃心穎v陳靜(非)<br />\n(冠)麥美恩v王敏奕(乙)<br />\n(甲)黃智雯v朱晨麗(甲)<br />\n(乙)胡琳v陳潔玲(乙)<br />\n(冠)沈卓盈v姚子羚(甲)<br />\n(乙)蔡思貝v林泳淘(冠)<br />\n(甲)李施嬅v陳法拉(冠)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e267956b78e28fab0b43f3e821cd618035640239","tid":434824,"uid":92376,"like":10,"dislike":36,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:00:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港女神總會盃第一圈</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名(非聯賽者則以非聯表示)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-10-14 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/YmuflgT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYmuflgT.png&h=080699f9&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gT3yZK6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgT3yZK6.png&h=9032c6bb&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(甲8)張沛樂vs鄧洢玲(非聯)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"c9a7787f492f1398b887a112c1f017bb6cc6f770","tid":434824,"uid":92376,"like":16,"dislike":34,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-10-14 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Rh0DRqr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRh0DRqr.png&h=bad80550&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ro6JrCy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRo6JrCy.png&h=6133d59e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(冠11)黃心穎vs陳靜(非聯)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"928f7cadd6be47d334abbeaa1d33c4827feedcbb","tid":434824,"uid":92376,"like":18,"dislike":35,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T16:03:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-10-14 12:04am-10:04pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gRlkZ88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgRlkZ88.png&h=5d25e391&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gcM73jk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgcM73jk.png&h=dc05bd20&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(冠12)麥美恩vs王敏奕(乙3)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div st